short leave my guns?

00:03.537 --> 00:05.504
-Hey!
-(gunshot)

00:05.539 --> 00:07.439
You ever see any of
these guys at the warehouse?

00:07.475 --> 00:08.674
-No.
-No?

00:08.709 --> 00:10.476
-This is about my son!
-(gunshot)

00:10.511 --> 00:12.378
PERSON: Oh--

00:12.413 --> 00:15.914
I didn't see anything, I swear,
but I did see something here.

00:15.950 --> 00:17.549
And how is it
we're missing some merchandise?

00:17.585 --> 00:19.918
No one steals from us, Jimmy.

00:19.954 --> 00:21.520
(gunshots)

00:21.555 --> 00:24.423
After I finish here today,
I want out of our arrangement.

00:24.458 --> 00:25.591
But the second
you're out on your own,

00:25.626 --> 00:26.825
I can no longer protect you.

00:26.861 --> 00:29.028
I lied.
you were born in Manila.

00:29.063 --> 00:30.496
<i> JAZ: I think Luca's sick.</i>

00:30.531 --> 00:33.866
He's dying.
He almost didn't make it, Fi.

