<i> ♪ 'Cause I only need</i>
<i> my crew plus me ♪</i>

01:06.033 --> 01:07.099
<i> ♪ All night, all night ♪</i>

01:07.134 --> 01:10.102
<i> (upbeat music)</i>

01:10.137 --> 01:13.072
(laughs) I don't know what it
is--I can't stop watching.

01:13.107 --> 01:14.239
Well, let me know if you

01:14.275 --> 01:15.541
want to do something
more than just watch.

01:15.576 --> 01:17.776
I'd be happy
to provide a private room.

01:19.013 --> 01:21.313
(chuckles)
Thanks, Arman, but...

01:21.348 --> 01:23.949
I couldn't do that to Isabel.
I'm crazy about her.

01:23.984 --> 01:25.284
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

01:25.319 --> 01:27.386
-Arman.
-Hey.

01:27.421 --> 01:30.756
Ben, hey.
Welcome to the family.

01:30.791 --> 01:32.758
(chuckles)

01:32.793 --> 01:34.626
You remember,
you hurt my sister,

01:34.662 --> 01:35.894
I'm gonna take you
to the desert

01:35.930 --> 01:37.463
and I'm gonna shoot you.

01:37.498 --> 01:40.265
BOTH: (chuckle)

01:40.301 --> 01:43.435
They'll never find you.
All right.

01:43.471 --> 01:44.803
Ladies.

01:44.839 --> 01:46.939
-PATRON: Whoo-whoo!
-(background chatter)

01:46.974 --> 01:48.307
Looks like my buddy Greg

01:48.342 --> 01:49.675
-had a few too many.
-Yeah.

01:49.710 --> 01:51.009
Whoo!
Whoa--

01:51.045 --> 01:52.778
-Oh--
-Oh!

